</s><s>Endospores are produced; the endospores are spherical and subterminal to terminal and do not swell the sporangia.</s><s>Obligately anaerobic.</s><s>Glucose and some other sugars are fermented.</s><s>The fermentation products from glucose are acetate, isobutyrate, isovalerate, valerate, lactate, and ethanol.</s><s>Xylan is degraded.</s><s>Cellulose is not degraded.</s><s>Thermophilic (temperature range, approximately 37 to 80Â°C).</s><s>Unable to grow autotrophically or to produce sulfur from thiosulfate.</s><s>The G+C content of the DNA is 37 mol%.</s><s>The type species is <i>Caloramator fervidus</i>.</s></p></content></protolog>